---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="width-constrained-container column-container gap-xl">
    <section class="column-container my-photo-container">
      <Image
        alt="Portrait of Ferry To"
        src={FerryPortrait}
        class="my-photo photo"
      />
      <p class="text-item-title greeting">
        👋 Hi! I'm Ferry. Nice to meet you. 😀
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="column-container">
      <h1 class="text-section-title">🧑‍💻 About Me</h1>
      <div class="column-container gap-lg">
        <Divider />
        {
          about_me_content.map((content) => (
            <span class="text-body" set:html={content} />
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <details>
        <summary class="text-section-title">
          <h2>🎤 Activities</h2>
        </summary>
        <div class="column-container gap-lg">
          <Divider />
          <h3 class="text-item-title">🎙️ Latest Public Events</h3>
          <ul class="text-body">
            {
              recent_activities.map((activity) => (
                <li>
                  <a href={activity.link} target="_blank">
                    {activity.title}
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
    <section>
      <details class="column-container">
        <summary class="text-section-title">
          <h2>🚀 Career</h2>
        </summary>
        <div class="column-container gap-lg">
          <Divider />
          <span class="text-body">I won’t go into every detail here — you can find the full record on my LinkedIn below.</span>
          {
            career_items.map((item) => (
              <div class="column-container gap-lg">
                <h3 class="text-item-title">{item.period}</h3>
                <span class="text-body">{item.description}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
    <section>
      <details class="column-container">
        <summary class="text-section-title">
          <h2>🏗️ Tools</h2>
        </summary>
        <div class="column-container gap-lg">
          <Divider />
          <span class="text-body">
            I started learning C# since 1.0 around 2002. Before the death of
            Flash, I was a rare certified ActionScript developer and won some
            competitions with C++.
          </span>
          {
            what_i_use.map((item) => (
              <div class="column-container gap-lg">
                <h3 class="text-item-title">{item.key}</h3>
                <ul class="text-body">
                  {item.value.map((subItem) => (
                    <li>
                      <b>{subItem.key}:</b> {subItem.value}
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
    <section>
      <details class="column-container">
        <summary class="text-section-title"><h2>🏠 Family</h2></summary>
        <div class="column-container gap-lg">
          <Divider />
          <h3 class="text-item-title">👰‍♀️ My Wife Elaine</h3>
          <div class="text-body">
            Elaine is a lovely, cheerful and clever lady. She is good at driving
            🚗 and cooking 🍳. She is my best friend who knows me better than
            anyone since I met her when she was twenty. She married with me at age
            just twenty-four, giving me so much love and support for all the
            years.
          </div>
          <div class="cat-photo-container column-container">
            <Image
              alt="Image of my wife Elaine with me, celebrating my birthday"
              src={BirthdayPhoto}
              class="family-photo photo"
            />
            <span class="text-item-subtitle">Elaine and I, celebrating my birthday.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="column-container gap-lg">
            <h3 class="text-item-title">🐈 My Cats</h3>
            {
              cats.map((cat) => (
                <span class="text-body">
                  {cat.name} — {cat.description}
                </span>
              ))
            }
          </div>
          <div class="cats-photo-grid">
            {
              cats.map((cat) => (
                <div class="cat-photo-container column-container">
                  <Image
                    alt={cat.alt}
                    src={cat.photo}
                    class="cat-photo photo"
                  />
                  <span class="text-item-subtitle">{cat.name}</span>
                </div>
              ))
            }
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
    <section>
      <details class="column-container">
        <summary class="text-section-title"><h2>👾 Hobbies</h2></summary>
        <div class="column-container gap-lg">
          <Divider />
          <h3 class="text-item-title">👫🏻 Hobbies with my wife</h3>
          <span class="text-body">🎥 We enjoy cinema trips and Netflix at home.</span>
          <span class="text-body">🏞️ We like short walks around lakes and parks.</span>
          <span class="text-body">
            🏓 Table tennis has been my favorite since primary school. After a
            20-year break, I’m back at it—we play a few times a week at
            <b><a href="https://www.centremk.com/" target="_blank">centre:mk</a></b>.
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-item-title">🎮 Video Games</h3>
          <span class="text-body">
            Age of Empires II, Minecraft and League of Legends are our all time
            favorites. I also spent significant time of my youth in World of
            Warcraft, StarCraft and Diablo series.
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-item-title">📚 Other Hobbies</h3>
          <span class="text-body"
            >Magic: The Gathering TCG since 1995; building Gundam model kits on
            holidays; bedtime reads of technical books and comics; and plenty of
            cat-patting. 🐈🐈🐈</span
          >
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
    <section>
      <details class="column-container">
        <summary class="text-section-title">
          <h2>📫 Connect</h2>
        </summary>
        <div class="column-container gap-lg">
          <Divider />
          <h3 class="text-item-title">
            Follow my latest news from my profiles.
          </h3>

          <div class="text-item-subtitle hide-on-mobile">
            {
              social_links.map((link, idx) => (
                <><a href={link.url} target="_blank">{link.name}</a>{idx < social_links.length - 1 && " | "}</>
              ))
            }
          </div>

          <div class="social-links-mobile hide-on-desktop column-container text-item-subtitle">
            <ul>
              {
                social_links.map((link) => (
                  <li><a href={link.url} target="_blank">{link.name}</a></li>
                ))
              }
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-item-title">Have an idea that needs a pragmatic architect? Let’s chat.</h3>
          <a
            href="mailto:ferry@verdantsparks.io"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-item-subtitle">ferry@verdantsparks.io</a
          >
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
  </div>
  <style>
    @import "../styles/typography.css";
    @import "../styles/spacing.css";
    @import "../styles/effect.css";
    @import "../styles/layout.css";
    @import "../styles/theme.css";

    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--gap-sm);
    }

    summary h2 {
      margin: 0;
      display: inline;
    }

    /* Ensure consistent marker positioning across browsers */
    summary::marker {
      content: "";
    }

    summary::before {
      content: "▶";
      display: inline-block;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    details[open] summary::before {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .gap-lg {
      gap: var(--gap-lg);
    }

    .gap-xl {
      gap: var(--gap-xl);
    }

    .column-container ul {
      line-height: 2;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .photo {
      border-radius: var(--corner-md);
    }

    .my-photo-container {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .my-photo {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 256px;
      max-width: 320px;
      height: auto;
    }

    .family-photo {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 256px;
      max-width: 512px;
      height: auto;
    }

    .cats-photo-grid {
      display: grid;
      width: 100%;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--gap-md);
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .cat-photo-container {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cat-photo {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 192px;
      max-width: 256px;
      max-height: 256px;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
    }

    .width-constrained-container {
      margin: auto;
      padding: var(--gap-lg);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .social-links-mobile ul {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .social-links-mobile li {
        margin: var(--gap-lg) 0;
      }

      .cats-photo-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: var(--gap-lg);
      }

      .cat-photo {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        max-height: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
